All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
Actor
The parent node for all child nodes to be displayed in the Scene graph of the game.
Animal
Animal holds a playable character that handle KeyEvents (WASD or ArrowKeys) from the user.
Bg
Bg provides a background image that fits the application window.
Car
Car provides a Car image obstacle in the game.
CurrentLevel
A class that sets and returns the current Level
Digit
Digit provides the image of numbers in the game.
Director
The Director class handles the stage and directs all scenes and points to the necessary scenes.
DisplayHiScore
Creates a popup window with the name of the Player and their highscore along with the previous Highscores of different PLayers.
End
End provides the Home images for when the Animal(Frog) reaches the end point.
HighScore
Provides the name and score of the Player who won and sorts it so that the Highest Score would appear at the top.
InfoScene
The InfoScene is a scene to display the info page.
LevelEight
Eighth Level of the game
LevelFive
Fifth Level of the game
LevelFour
Fourth Level of the game
LevelGenerator
LevelGenerator is an abstract class that holds all of the child nodes for different levels.
LevelNine
Ninth Level of the game
LevelOne
First Level of the game
LevelSeven
Seventh Level of the game
LevelSix
Sixth Level of the game
LevelTen
Tenth Level of the game
LevelThree
Third Level of the game
LevelTwo
Second Level of the game
Log
Log provides a Log image platform of different types/sizes for the Frogger to jump on in the game.
Main
Main is the entry point in which the Application can perform what a JavaFX application does.
MenuScene
The MenuScene is a scene to display the Main Menu.
mp3Player
mp3Player handles all media Playing instances.
myButton
Provides a custom Button image.
Obstacle
The parent node for all obstacles (nodes that makes the Frogger die).
Platform
The parent node for all Platforms (nodes that the Frogger can stand on).
SetHiScore
Read and Writes scores from and into CSV files.
SpeedGenerator
SpeedGenerator is an abstract class that generates the speed responsible for each level.
Truck
Truck provides a Truck image obstacle in either short trucks or long trucks.
Turtle
Turtle provides a Turtle image platform that swims for the Frogger to jump on in the game.
WetTurtle
WetTurtle provides a WetTurtle image platform that swims and sinks for the Frogger to jump on when its floating in the game.
World
World is the base abstract class that holds all branch nodes in the Scene of the game.
